            <div type="bibliography">
                <p><bibl><ptr target="iplik2010"/> <citedRange></citedRange></bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="feisselBE"/> <citedRange>2013.517</citedRange></bibl>,  
                    <bibl><ptr target="seg"/> <citedRange unit="entry">60.1557</citedRange></bibl>, 
                    </p>
            </div>
            
            <div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
               <ab><lb n="1"/><w lemma="αὐξάνω">Αὔξη</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τὸ</w> <orgName ref="#green" nymRef="#μέρος τῶν Πρασίνων"><w lemma="μέρος">μέροϲ</w>
                    <lb n="2"/><w lemma="ὁ">τῶν</w> <w lemma="πράσινος">Πραϲί
                    <lb n="3" break="no"/>νων</w></orgName> <w lemma="ὅπου">ὅπου</w>
                   <lb n="4"/> <w lemma="φθόνος">φθόνοϲ</w>
                    <lb n="5"/><w lemma="οὐκ">οὐχ</w> <w lemma="ἅπτω">ἅπτε-
                    <lb n="6" break="no"/><space quantity="2" unit="character"></space> τε</w> <space quantity="2" unit="character"></space>
               </ab>
             </div> 
           
            
           <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#cmr"><p>Up with the party of the Greens, where Envy does not have a hold!</p>
           </div>
                <div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" source="#feisselBE"><p>Vive le parti des Verts, où l’Envie n’a pas de prise!</p>
           </div>
                <div type="translation" xml:lang="de" source="#iplik2010"><p>Wachse, Partei der Grünen, wo sich kein Neid anheftet!</p> </div>
                    <div type="translation" xml:lang="tr" source="#iplik2010"><p>Kıskançlığa yer olmayan Yeşiller'in Partisi, güçlen!</p>
           </div>
         
            <div type="commentary">
                <p></p>
                <p>The idea of Phthonos, envy, as grasping at that which is good is very well-established - so e.g. Plutarch De invidia 537 F.3: 
                    ὁ φθόνος ἅπτεται μάλιστα τῶν χρηστῶν (available at <ref target="http://data.perseus.org/citations/urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg105.perseus-grc1:537f">Perseus</ref>)</p>
            </div>
            
